HEADWORD: Grysbok
<hw>Grys"bok</hw> <pr>(?)</pr> <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[D.
<ets>grijs</ets> gray + <ets>bok</ets> buck.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>A small South African antelope (<spn>Neotragus melanotis</spn>). It
is speckled with gray and chestnut, above; the under parts are reddish
fawn.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

